ds." Eur J Clin Pharmacol 48 (1995): 367-71[5] Min DI, Ku YM, Geraets DR, Lee HC "Effect of grapefruit juice on the pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of quinidine in healthy volunteers." J Clin Pharmacol 36 (1996): 469-76', 1767369485);
